*The intersection of ecosystem threat status and protection level reveals protected areas expansion priorities and challenges in Fynbos, Grassland and Desert Biomes.*

![The Endangered Black Harrier: an iconic species of the highly threatened renosterveld ecosystems of the Fynbos Biome (Â© Odette Curtis-Scott)](./imgs/blackharrier_crop_ocs.png)

::::: columns
